-- Sands China Says It May Get Approval for Macau Apartment Sales This Year
-- Mark Lee
-- 2010-06-19T07:47:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-19/sands-china-says-it-may-get-approval-for-macau-apartment-sales-this-year.html

          
          
             Sands China Ltd. may get approval
from the Macau government for sales at its hotel apartment
project in the city this year, Chief Executive Officer Steve
Jacobs said in an interview after the company’s annual meeting
in Hong Kong today.  
 The company has applied for approval for the sales at the
Four Seasons-managed “co-op” project, Jacobs said.  
